<P>
   CUBANS-PRISON-DEAL _ U.S. government officials ended a tense
hostage standoff at a Louisiana prison by striking a deal with the
Cuban government that will permit the Cuban inmates at the center
of the uprising to be deported to Havana, federal officials said
Sunday. By Marc Lacey with David Firestone.
</P>
