<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-20 15:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4349 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e BC-DIGITAL-LA-COLUMN-LAD     12-20 1332
