<P>
   For his part, Cicconi cited legal and technical issues that he
said could oblige AT&AMP;T to act as more than a neutral mail carrier
in cyberspace.
</P>
<P>
   One of them is the company's obligation to preserve copyright
protection, a particularly sensitive issue in the music field at a
time when it has become simple for computers to make perfect
digital copies.
</P>
<P>
   Yet another unresolved issue: How to deal with ``bandwidth
hogs'' _ customers who, say, seek to download a movie at a time
when their neighbors are also on line, thereby slowing down their
speed of Internet access.
</P>
<P>
   Andrew J. Glass's e-mail address is andyg(at)coxnews.com
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
<P>
   For Use By Clients of the New York Times News Service
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
