   BC-OBIT-MAHON-NYT (moved on Sunday, Dec. 19)
</P>
<P>
   The obituary of Jackson Barrett Mahon, sent by the New York
Times News Service on Sunday, Dec. 19, misspelled the surname of
the author of the book. He was Paul Brickhill, not Brickall.
</P>
