<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Wednesday, Dec.
15, about retailers who told a tax study commission that they
oppose making the Internet a tax-free zone included one company
erroneously among the group, known as the e-Fairness Coalition.
Federated Department Stores is not a member and does not agree with
the coalition's views.
