Quarter, one of the nation's oldest and best-preserved residential
districts, say it is being turned into a Disneyland entertainment
center catering to the 11 million annual tourists and the
businesses that feed off them. (Anne Rochell Konigsmark/Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT14) NEW YORK -- Dec. 20, 1999 -- BOMB-THEATER-REVIEW --
Jason Catalano, left, Erik Weiner and Jordan Allen-Dutton do
